{"tid":2055513,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗成為首位收入破10億美元足球員","createTime":"2020-06-08T04:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T18:18:32.000Z","uid":282509,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0d38eb441622b3af2be19c1b6dafab583a85a4ec","tid":2055513,"uid":282509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"35歲的C朗拿度加入高爾夫傳奇「老虎」活士和拳王美韋達，躋身累計收入逾10億美元的運動員行列，是足球壇第一人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgaMbkK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgaMbkK.jpg&h=2b701f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據《福布斯》公布，該祖雲達斯球星去年稅前收入1.05億美元，累計超過10億美元。他亦是2020年榜上第4收入高名人，排在網球名將費達拿、饒舌歌手Kanye West、女星 Kylie Jenner之後；至於美斯則排第5，尼馬第7。<br />\n<br />\n據報，C朗拿度17年職業球員生涯中賺取6.5億美元工資，此外還有不少廣告、贊助和代言等收入，自己也創立了時裝及生活品牌、酒店、博物館等商業王國。要不是因為新冠肺炎令人工縮水，這位葡萄牙球星2020年收入可能更多。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a8cba675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"1631cf8163b2d640b125a7a3bafb41b770ef26bf","tid":2055513,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 咪又係要打工"},{"pid":"e9d4b5b56607fd89222de60a5d71e3293bd3b5b6","tid":2055513,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"碧咸  以前都無咁多？"},{"pid":"ece64c6cc32abd8960fc87d1e375975123f4d924","tid":2055513,"uid":282509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9d4b5b56607fd89222de60a5d71e3293bd3b5b6","tid":2055513,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"碧咸  以前都無咁多？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"緊係冇"},{"pid":"e25e74a94b3e3e744624d8fd2faecbd3265fd3b8","tid":2055513,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"做咁多生意賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />